無論我們怎樣嘗試逃脫出來
And no matter how we try and escape,

821
01:01:50,640 --> 01:01:53,143
自救 看心理醫生 嗑藥
self-help, therapy, drugs,

822
01:01:53,209 --> 01:01:55,883
我們只會越陷越深
we just sink further and further down.

823
01:01:56,446 --> 01:01:59,017
只有一種方式才能真正地突破牢籠
The only way to truly break out of the box

824
01:01:59,082 --> 01:02:01,153
就是捨棄所有
is just to get rid of it altogether.

825
01:02:01,517 --> 01:02:04,498
我是說 你起初所鑄造的輝煌
I mean, you built it in the first place.

826
01:02:04,554 --> 01:02:08,229
如果你身邊的人都從精神上打擊你 輝煌又有何用
If the people around you are breaking your spirit, who needs them?

827
01:02:08,291 --> 01:02:10,771
老婆假裝愛你
Your wife who pretends to love you,

828
01:02:10,860 --> 01:02:12,669
兒子忍受不了你
your son who can't even stand you.

829
01:02:12,729 --> 01:02:15,232
我說 把他們的苦逼置於腦後吧
I mean, put them out of their misery.

830
01:02:15,298 --> 01:02:17,272
重新開始不可怕
Starting over isn't crazy.

831
01:02:19,202 --> 01:02:22,081
可怕的是日復一日
Crazy is being miserable

832
01:02:22,138 --> 01:02:25,243
變得苦逼 夢遊樣四處轉
and walking around half asleep, numb,

833
01:02:25,243 --> 01:02:27,714
麻木不仁
day after day after day.

834
01:02:27,777 --> 01:02:29,848
可怕的是假裝開心
Crazy is pretending to be happy.

835
01:02:31,214 --> 01:02:34,559
自己悲慘的餘生
Pretending that the way things are

836
01:02:34,617 --> 01:02:38,030
都不得不一直維持假裝的狀態生活
is the way they have to be for the rest of your bleeding life.

837
01:02:38,821 --> 01:02:41,461
所有潛在的希望
All the potential, hope,

838
01:02:41,557 --> 01:02:43,594
所有的愉悅 感受
all that joy, feeling,

839
01:02:43,659 --> 01:02:47,038
所有生活從你身上榨取的激情
all that passion that life has sucked out of you.

840
01:02:47,430 --> 01:02:49,603
伸出手 抓住它
Reach out, grab a hold of it

841
01:02:49,665 --> 01:02:53,613
然後從吸血的暴民手中奪回來
and snatch it back from that blood-sucking rabble.

842
01:02:56,405 --> 01:02:58,385
沃特 很高興你來接受採訪
Walter, it's good to have you here.

843
01:02:59,408 --> 01:03:00,751
謝謝
Thank you.

844
01:03:11,154 --> 01:03:14,363
這就是沃特.布萊克現在的寫照
This is a picture of Walter Black,

845
01:03:15,958 --> 01:03:18,268
一個絕望 沮喪的人
a hopelessly depressed individual

846
01:03:20,229 --> 01:03:23,369
他變身海貍先生
who becomes the Beaver,

847
01:03:23,432 --> 01:03:26,276
引發了一種風潮
who becomes a phenomenon.

848
01:03:26,369 --> 01:03:30,044
有很多人都非常渴望收聽
There's a lot of people out there who are desperate enough to listen.

849
01:03:30,940 --> 01:03:32,942
人們似乎都擁有
People seem to love a train wreck

850
01:03:33,442 --> 01:03:34,978
一種葉公好龍的心理
when it's not happening to them.

851
01:03:40,416 --> 01:03:42,919
諾拉 我們談談嘛
Norah, look, we need to talk.

852
01:03:42,985 --> 01:03:44,055
現在不是好時機
Now's not a good time.

853
01:03:44,120 --> 01:03:46,657
是啊 我給你打過電話 發過短信 還Q過你
Yeah, well, I called you, I texted you, and I IM'd you,

854
01:03:46,722 --> 01:03:48,565
從沒有時機對過的時候 所以
and it never seems like a good time. So...

855
01:03:48,624 --> 01:03:50,331
也許你該把這當成是一種暗示
Maybe you should take that as a hint.

856
01:03:50,426 --> 01:03:54,033
我是傻子 可以了吧 我也不想事情發展成這樣
I'm an idiot, all right? That's not how I wanted things to turn out.

857
01:03:54,130 --> 01:03:56,633
我喜歡你 好吧 我確實很在乎
I like you, all right? I actually give a shit.

858
01:03:56,699 --> 01:04:00,017
你不用在乎我 你甚至不瞭解我
You don't give a shit about me. You don't even know me.

859
01:04:00,017 --> 01:04:01,913
你哥哥死於吸毒過量 對吧
Look, your brother OD'd, all right?

860
01:04:01,971 --> 01:04:04,178
但是放棄自己的天賦 你成為現在這樣
But ditching your own talent, what makes you you,

861
01:04:04,273 --> 01:04:07,117
這也不會讓他起死回生 只會讓你一事無成
that's not gonna bring him back. It's just going to make you nothing.

862
01:04:07,610 --> 01:04:11,057
你他媽離我遠點
You stay the hell away from me.

863
01:04:11,147 --> 01:04:13,090
你和你一家的精神病
You and your psycho family.

864
01:04:27,396 --> 01:04:32,106
你開心嗎 你發自肺腑地開心嗎
Are you happy? Are you truly, truly happy?

865
01:04:32,268 --> 01:04:34,851
約翰 我們身上都缺少一樣東西
Because, Jon, there's something lacking in all of us.

866
01:04:34,851 --> 01:04:36,010
缺失了一塊
A missing piece.

867
01:04:36,072 --> 01:04:39,645
有一小塊黑點或是暗點
There's a little bit of a black spot or a dark spot.

868
01:04:39,809 --> 01:04:41,482
明顯嗎
It's that obvious?

869
01:04:42,812 --> 01:04:45,452
約翰 很抱歉這樣說 但沃特需要一些幫助
I'm sorry to say, Jon, but Walter needs a little help.

870
01:04:45,615 --> 01:04:48,255
因為他現在無法流利地表達出來
Because he's not too articulate at the moment.

871
01:04:48,317 --> 01:04:50,763
事實上 他的狀態很不好
In fact, he's not well.

872
01:05:01,230 --> 01:05:04,439
起床 起床
Get up. Get up.

873
01:05:07,236 --> 01:05:09,682
起來 你這個悲催的傢伙
Get up, you miserable wanker.

874
01:05:09,739 --> 01:05:13,084
你不會從沃特口中挖到太多話的
You're not going to get much out of ol' Walter.

875
01:05:13,142 --> 01:05:15,816
他有些感覺不適 瞭解沒
He's feeling a bit under the weather, you see?

876
01:05:15,912 --> 01:05:18,017
來吧 廣播節目而已
Come on. it's a radio show.

877
01:05:18,147 --> 01:05:20,559
人們又看不到玩偶
People can't even see the puppet.

878
01:05:20,616 --> 01:05:23,495
為什麼要通過玩偶講話呢
So why talk through the puppet?

879
01:06:36,500 --> 01:06:39,000
(相似點)

880
01:06:39,300 --> 01:06:40,700
(咬嘴唇)

881
01:06:41,000 --> 01:06:43,200
(按摩眉毛)

882
01:06:44,300 --> 01:06:47,200
(憎恨父親 代代如此)

883
01:07:36,685 --> 01:07:37,993
你好
Hello?

884
01:07:38,054 --> 01:07:39,055
小梅 是我
Mere, it's me.

885
01:07:39,355 --> 01:07:41,164
沃特 你沒事吧
Walter, are you okay?

886
01:07:41,223 --> 01:07:42,634
嗯 我說
Yeah, look,

887
01:07:43,325 --> 01:07:46,829
我不能 我不能
I can't I can't

888
01:07:46,896 --> 01:07:48,034
你在幹什麼
What are you doing?

889
01:07:50,066 --> 01:07:51,636
發生了什麼事
What's going on?

890
01:07:51,967 --> 01:07:53,844
沃特 沃特 講話啊
Walter? Walter, talk to me!

891
01:07:54,737 --> 01:07:57,911
你在和誰講電話
Who are you talking to?

892
01:07:58,240 --> 01:08:01,619
掛掉 現在就掛掉      沃特
Hang up. You hang up right now.        Walter?

893
01:08:07,983 --> 01:08:11,897
你媽會縫合吧
Can your mother stitch?

894
01:08:26,502 --> 01:08:29,415
你永遠都贏不了
You'll never win.

895
01:08:40,783 --> 01:08:43,662
我想要爸爸 爸爸在哪      我知道
I want Daddy. Where's Daddy?        I know.

896
01:08:43,719 --> 01:08:46,199
我想要海貍先生
I want the Beaver.

897
01:08:47,656 --> 01:08:50,637
還沒睡呢 親愛的 你去找你爸行麼
Are you awake? Honey, you've got to go get Dad, all right?

898
01:08:50,793 --> 01:08:52,101
為啥
Why?

899
01:08:52,161 --> 01:08:55,233
他不接電話 亨利也哭個不停
He's not answering his phone, and Henry won't stop crying.

900
01:08:55,297 --> 01:08:58,540
我都不知道怎麼辦是好 求你了
I just don't know what to do. Please.

901
01:08:58,601 --> 01:09:02,447
來 寶貝 我們一會就去找爸爸 不哭了啊
Come on, baby. We're going to find Daddy soon. it's okay.

902
01:09:50,486 --> 01:09:55,595
我沒有給你你想要的東西嗎
Haven't I given you exactly what you asked for?

903
01:10:02,565 --> 01:10:04,738
你不需要家人 沃特
You don't need them, Walter.

904
01:10:11,707 --> 01:10:13,084
我愛你
I love you.

905
01:10:16,812 --> 01:10:20,316
我才是那個深深 深深愛著你的人
I'm the only one that really, really loves you.

906
01:10:21,951 --> 01:10:27,697
所以我才不會讓你回到以前的生活
And that is why I would never let you go back.

907
01:10:31,961 --> 01:10:33,770
永遠不會
Never.

908
01:10:46,742 --> 01:10:49,086
我不想睡覺了
I don't want to sleep anymore.

909
01:10:51,380 --> 01:10:52,381
也許
Maybe...

910
01:10:54,183 --> 01:10:56,493
也許我們該做點什麼
Maybe, you know, we should work on something.

911
01:10:59,855 --> 01:11:03,894
好的 同伴 來吧
Yeah, sure, mate. Come on.

912
01:11:17,306 --> 01:11:19,308
沃特 不要這樣
Walter, not like this.

913
01:11:19,375 --> 01:11:20,786
不要這樣
Don't do it.

914
01:11:20,876 --> 01:11:22,910
情況會比以往糟糕 要糟糕得多
It will be worse than before. Much worse.

915
01:11:22,911 --> 01:11:26,586
你最後想變成一坨孤零零 毫無價值的屎嗎
Do you want to end up a worthless, lonely piece of shit?

916
01:11:28,517 --> 01:11:30,588
沒有我你就是個廢物 沃特
You're nothing without me, Walter.

917
01:11:31,487 --> 01:11:32,488
廢物
Nothing!

918
01:11:33,322 --> 01:11:35,056
我只是你的一部分
I'm the only part of you that works.

919
01:11:43,332 --> 01:11:45,005
很抱歉
I'm sorry.

920
01:12:00,516 --> 01:12:03,832
沃特 你還記得你的兒子亨利嗎
Walter! How about Henry, your kid? You remember him?

921
01:12:04,386 --> 01:12:05,797
沃特
Walter!

922
01:12:08,891 --> 01:12:10,029
爸爸
Dad?

923
01:12:12,328 --> 01:12:15,118
血壓正在下降 等上了手術台再動止血帶
BP's dropping. Don't touch the tourniquet until he's on the table.

924
01:12:15,531 --> 01:12:17,568
這是他還有脈搏的原因
It's the only reason he still has a pulse.

925
01:12:23,972 --> 01:12:25,645
醒來
Wake

926
01:12:26,942 --> 01:12:29,115
*從睡夢中醒來*
*From your sleep*

927
01:12:31,780 --> 01:12:38,459
*擦乾眼淚*
*The drying of your tears*

928
01:12:39,388 --> 01:12:44,599
*我們逃離了當下*
*Today we escape*

929
01:12:45,627 --> 01:12:47,800
作為傑瑞公司的新CEO
As the new CEO of Jerry Co. ,

930
01:12:48,897 --> 01:12:52,777
我向大家保證公司已經交由可靠之人管理
I want to assure people that the company is back in good hands.

931
01:12:55,738 --> 01:12:57,479
*收好行囊*
*Pack*

932
01:12:58,607 --> 01:13:01,349
*整好衣裳*
*And get dressed*

933
01:13:03,145 --> 01:13:09,926
*在你父親聽到我們之前*
*Before your father hears us*

934
01:13:10,886 --> 01:13:13,366
*在*
*Before*

935
01:13:14,256 --> 01:13:16,668
*地獄之門*
*All hell*

936
01:13:18,627 --> 01:13:22,336
*開啟之前*
*Breaks loose*

937
01:13:47,523 --> 01:13:49,662
我給了珀特200塊
I paid Porter $200,

938
01:13:51,827 --> 01:13:54,000
他去做了調查
and he did some research.

939
01:13:54,096 --> 01:13:56,372
我辜負了家人的期望
I let my family down.

940
01:13:57,633 --> 01:13:58,976
我對此感到非常慚愧
I'm really ashamed about this,

941
01:13:58,977 --> 01:14:02,255
我想讓這件事盡快過去
and I just want to put it behind me as soon as possible.

942
01:14:03,100 --> 01:14:05,700
尊敬的珀特 布朗大學招生辦很遺憾地通知你

943
01:14:05,700 --> 01:14:08,900
由於近來的一些事宜 你的大學錄取被取消
請來年再申

944
01:14:10,179 --> 01:14:14,022
孩子 你在蓮花池裡釣魚嗎
Grasshopper, are you fishing in our lily pond?

945
01:14:14,049 --> 01:14:16,086
走吧 咱去探望下你爸爸
Come on. Let's go see your dad.

946
01:14:18,787 --> 01:14:20,664
我不去      好吧
I'm not going.        Fine.

947
01:14:20,956 --> 01:14:22,572
如果你不想去就不去 
If you don't want to go, then don't go. 

948
01:14:22,573 --> 01:14:24,238
但你也不能成天睡覺啊
But you're not just going to sleep all day.

949
01:14:26,028 --> 01:14:27,029
來吧
Come on.

950
01:14:27,963 --> 01:14:29,840
來 珀特 起來 咱們走
Come on, Porter. Let's go. Get up!

951
01:14:29,898 --> 01:14:30,899
看在上帝的份上      住手
For Christ's sake.        Stop!

952
01:14:30,966 --> 01:14:32,946
我們走嗎      別動我
Are we going?        Stop! Stop!

953
01:14:33,535 --> 01:14:34,536
好的
Yes.

954
01:14:35,671 --> 01:14:36,775
隨你了
Fine.

955
01:14:39,475 --> 01:14:42,115
找點事做 行嗎
Just do something, all right?

956
01:14:42,177 --> 01:14:45,386
出去散個步 偷輛車 我都不管
Go outside, take a walk, steal a car. I don't care.

957
01:14:45,447 --> 01:14:48,485
我回家時不想看到你還躺在床上
I just don't want to find you back in bed when I get home.

958
01:15:00,095 --> 01:15:01,870
你的家人來了
Your family's here.

959
01:15:15,410 --> 01:15:17,412
沒事的 去吧
It's okay. Go on.

960
01:15:23,085 --> 01:15:25,224
嗨 小傢伙 你好嗎
Hey, little fella. How are you?

961
01:15:25,988 --> 01:15:27,092
好
Good.

962
01:15:27,723 --> 01:15:28,861
這是什麼呀
What's that?

963
01:15:29,691 --> 01:15:32,475
這是個腦子      哇 是腦子呢
it's a brain.        Wow. it's a brain!

964
01:15:32,928 --> 01:15:34,965
媽媽說你的大腦壞掉了
Mom says yours got broken.

965
01:15:35,364 --> 01:15:37,401
這個正能派上用場
This will come in handy.

966
01:15:37,499 --> 01:15:41,413
這麼說 你瘋了嗎
So, are you crazy?

967
01:15:42,871 --> 01:15:44,873
也許吧
Maybe.

968
01:15:44,973 --> 01:15:46,213
我們正在這治療
We're working on it.

969
01:15:47,175 --> 01:15:50,054
這意味著你能回家嗎
Does that mean you can come home?

970
01:15:50,112 --> 01:15:51,629
這一點我們也正在努力
We're working on that, too.

971
01:15:52,214 --> 01:15:53,488
你哥哥呢
Hey, where's your brother?

972
01:15:54,550 --> 01:15:58,088
可能在睡覺 他一直在睡覺
Probably sleeping. It's all he does.

973
01:16:00,923 --> 01:16:02,300
過來
Come here.

974
01:16:03,225 --> 01:16:05,967
過來 我要咬你的耳朵
Come here! I'll bite you on your ear!

975
01:16:13,800 --> 01:16:17,200
(睡覺)

976
01:16:43,100 --> 01:16:45,900
(這兒見 拜託!)

977
01:16:57,679 --> 01:16:58,953
喔
Wow.

978
01:17:00,349 --> 01:17:02,590
我給你發了15條短信
I must have sent you 15 texts.

979
01:17:03,385 --> 01:17:05,228
我都放棄了
I'd given up on you.

980
01:17:06,722 --> 01:17:10,795
彼此彼此吧
Well, that makes two of us.

981
01:17:12,194 --> 01:17:16,006
你說得對 我的確是想要傾訴
You were right. I guess I had some stuff to say.

982
01:17:18,433 --> 01:17:20,936
顯然 有很多東西想要表達
Apparently, a lot of stuff.

983
01:17:23,038 --> 01:17:24,784
不管怎樣 你現在知道我的想法 
Anyway, now you know what's on my mind, 

984
01:17:24,784 --> 01:17:26,509
這樣就可以寫演講稿了
so you can write my speech.

985
01:17:26,642 --> 01:17:28,485
不行
No.

986
01:17:28,577 --> 01:17:31,217
我想我已經正式退出代寫這一行了
I think I'm officially out of that business.

987
01:17:31,380 --> 01:17:32,791
你還欠我一篇演講稿
You owe me.

988
01:17:36,084 --> 01:17:38,257
這是你為我畫的
You made this for me.

989
01:17:38,920 --> 01:17:40,695
昨天畫的
Yesterday.

990
01:17:41,423 --> 01:17:43,061
為什麼呢
How come?

991
01:17:43,191 --> 01:17:45,193
因為牆上的內容遠遠要多於
Because there's more that belongs on a wall than,

992
01:17:46,828 --> 01:17:49,206
"諾拉有個死鬼哥哥"
"Norah has a dead brother. "

993
01:17:51,366 --> 01:17:52,777
即使是一團亂
Even if it is a big mess.

994
01:17:54,469 --> 01:17:55,777
畫得很好啊
It's amazing.

995
01:17:57,706 --> 01:18:01,677
有意思 我覺得畫了坨屎 你覺得畫得很好
Funny. I think it's a mess, and you think it's amazing.

996
01:18:01,743 --> 01:18:04,417
我覺得你很棒 你卻覺得自己什麼都不是
And I think you're amazing, and you think you're a mess.

997
01:18:06,515 --> 01:18:10,088
你知道麼 我不想再思考了
You know what? I don't want to think anymore.

998
01:18:15,223 --> 01:18:17,669
你仍欠我一篇演講稿
You still owe me a speech.

999
01:18:18,393 --> 01:18:20,532
一定要保證像我的口氣
Just make sure it sounds like me.

1000
01:18:27,836 --> 01:18:32,649
那麼我是坐這寫然後再被逮捕一次呢
So, do I just sit here writing and get arrested again?

1001
01:18:32,708 --> 01:18:35,279
不用 你拿走吧 笨蛋
No, take it with you, dummy.

1002
01:18:35,677 --> 01:18:38,624
我拿走?
Take it with me?

1003
01:19:23,892 --> 01:19:26,998
畢業生們 死去的詩人們
Good afternoon, graduates, dead poets,

1004
01:19:27,129 --> 01:19:31,373
畫家們 未來的愛因斯坦們 下午好
painters, future Einsteins, and all those in between.

1005
01:19:31,867 --> 01:19:35,212
今天我站在這裡 警告大家有人在對你們說謊
Today I'm here to warn you that you are being lied to.

1006
01:19:35,337 --> 01:19:40,218
父母 老師 醫生都對我們撒了謊
Our parents, our teachers, our doctors have lied to us.

1007
01:19:40,308 --> 01:19:45,417
說的都是同一句謊言 就6個字
And it's the exact same lie. The same six words,

1008
01:19:45,514 --> 01:19:47,994
"一切都會好的"
"Everything is going to be okay. "

1009
01:19:50,018 --> 01:19:51,793
但要是好不了呢
But what if it isn't?

1010
01:19:53,288 --> 01:19:55,894
要是有些體驗是遺傳來的
What if some of human experience is just something you inherit,

1011
01:19:55,957 --> 01:19:58,767
就像卷髮或是碧眼一樣
like curly hair or blue eyes?

1012
01:19:58,827 --> 01:20:03,503
要是你生來就痛苦 生來就是一樁悲劇呢
What if pain is just in your DNA and tragedy is your birthright?

1013
01:20:04,933 --> 01:20:05,934
又或者
Or what if..

1014
01:20:06,001 --> 01:20:08,777
或者有時      有時
"Or what if sometimes... "        ... sometimes...

1015
01:20:08,937 --> 01:20:11,816
...突然之間 它成了你的最低期望
"... right out of the blue, when you least expect it,

1016
01:20:12,674 --> 01:20:15,120
破事就發生了呢
"shit just happens?

1017
01:20:17,412 --> 01:20:19,221
破事就發生了呢
"Shit just happens. "

1018
01:20:22,217 --> 01:20:24,163
好吧 我保證 現在大家都在想
Okay, I'm sure, right now, you're all thinking,

1019
01:20:24,219 --> 01:20:27,108
靠 這是我聽過的最黑暗的畢業生演講
"Man, this is the darkest graduation speech I've ever heard. "

1020
01:20:27,722 --> 01:20:30,703
是的 我同意你們的意見 但這不是我寫的
And it is. I agree with you, but I didn't write it.

1021
01:20:35,063 --> 01:20:40,172
我花了很長時間等待謊言成真
I've spent so much time waiting for this lie to come true

1022
01:20:40,235 --> 01:20:43,910
所以我付錢讓別人來替我說出真相
that I finally paid someone to tell the truth for me.

1023
01:20:47,342 --> 01:20:48,878
我並不好
I'm not okay.

1024
01:20:49,411 --> 01:20:50,890
一點都不好
Not at all.

1025
01:20:53,281 --> 01:20:55,557
真相是
The truth is,

1026
01:20:55,617 --> 01:20:57,893
我缺失了一樣東西
I'm missing something,

1027
01:20:59,588 --> 01:21:01,124
是我的最愛
the thing I loved the most,

1028
01:21:02,390 --> 01:21:05,371
是一張我希望他就在前排坐著的面龐
the face I wish were in the front row right now.

1029
01:21:07,729 --> 01:21:10,437
我永遠都回不來的哥哥
The brother I'll never get back.

1030
01:21:15,537 --> 01:21:17,608
那麼我該怎麼做
So what do I do with that?

1031
01:21:21,243 --> 01:21:23,314
我們大家會怎麼做
What do any of us do,

1032
01:21:24,246 --> 01:21:26,248
除了說謊以外
besides lie?

1033
01:21:29,551 --> 01:21:31,690
我相信的是
This is what I believe.

1034
01:21:35,290 --> 01:21:40,035
現在禮堂裡 有人正與你一起
Right now, in this auditorium, there is someone who is with you.

1035
01:21:40,095 --> 01:21:44,475
他願意來接你 彈去你身上的灰塵
Someone who is willing to pick you up, dust you off,

1036
01:21:44,532 --> 01:21:45,806
親吻你 原諒你
kiss you, forgive you,

1037
01:21:46,768 --> 01:21:50,079
容忍你 等著你 陪著你
put up with you, wait for you, carry you,

1038
01:21:50,438 --> 01:21:51,849
愛著你
love you.

1039
01:21:54,175 --> 01:21:57,019
雖然事事不會一直都順利
So, while everything may not always be okay,

1040
01:21:57,946 --> 01:22:00,119
但有一點我相信是真的
one thing I know is true.

1041
01:22:01,783 --> 01:22:04,195
你沒有必要一個人戰鬥
You do not have to be alone.

1042
01:22:46,661 --> 01:22:49,141
我沒想到你會來
I didn't think you'd come.

1043
01:22:49,397 --> 01:22:51,775
我也沒想到自己會來
I didn't think I would, either.

1044
01:22:59,574 --> 01:23:01,451
我很高興你還活著
I'm just glad you're still here.

1045
01:23:03,311 --> 01:23:05,188
我身體的大部分是還活著
Yeah, most of me, anyway.

1046
01:23:05,780 --> 01:23:07,316
嗯
Yeah.

1047
01:23:12,454 --> 01:23:14,434
你知道嗎 我還是個孩子的時候
You know, when I was a little kid,

1048
01:23:14,923 --> 01:23:18,336
我滿心期望就是像你一樣
man, all I ever wanted was to be like you.

1049
01:23:21,396 --> 01:23:22,875
之後我長大了
Then I got older,

1050
01:23:25,533 --> 01:23:28,309
我又想成為別人
and I just wanted to be anybody else.

1051
01:23:35,043 --> 01:23:36,044
現在呢
And now?

1052
01:23:42,517 --> 01:23:43,621
爸爸
Dad.

1053
01:24:41,309 --> 01:24:43,755
這是沃特·布萊克現在的寫照
This is a picture of Walter Black,

1054
01:24:45,480 --> 01:24:48,120
他曾不得不成為海貍先生
who had to become a beaver,

1055
01:24:48,183 --> 01:24:50,663
也不得不為人父
who had to become a father,

1056
01:24:51,953 --> 01:24:53,337
因此有朝一日 
so that, one day, 

1057
01:24:53,800 --> 01:24:57,461
這可能正是沃特·布萊克一生的寫照
this might just be a picture of Walter Black.

